Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:26.54,op kara,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream of life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:19.39,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The fight doesn't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:25.64,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder how far I've come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:30.94,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:37.45,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:44.08,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:50.42,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(0,751)}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:59.14,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:05.39,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I fuel my passion until I succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:12.15,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There will be meetings and partings along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:18.40,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I'll simply believe in my strength that you've taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:24.29,op trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And rise back up again and again and again
