Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:54.72,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In this world, every day is dull and full of nonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:23:00.31,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I cover my ears, trying to mute the noise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:07.57,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do people hurt each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.03,0:23:18.87,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the contradictory, overlapping shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:22.88,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}on the recesses of my heart, fallen into despair
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.46,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}While carrying this pain in my chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:28.55,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}can I really dream of tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:35.47,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Remembering the rainbow I found after the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:42.10,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I close my eyes; come fly with me into my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:45.57,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I have you, who shines so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:50.90,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can envision an everlasting rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:58.83,ed trans,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And even remember the moonlight that lit us the night we met
